Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.95,0:01:33.59,a,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}{\pos(640,470)}風的答復
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.29,0:01:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.46,0:01:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是被這裡的酒給吸引來的而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑 該不會想說你也是這家伙的鹡鸰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 她是…真的和我一點關系都沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.27,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 別對她出手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.76,0:01:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 羅嗦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.98,0:02:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰翅 稍微教訓下他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記…叫別人錄高畫質的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.13,0:02:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.51,0:02:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花小姐 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到 到底在哪裡啊 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.85,0:02:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 你辦完事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是辦事的時候 皆人被懲罰部隊的拐走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盤子…碎了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:38.94,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（讀音和拐走了一樣）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.08,0:02:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帝都碼頭5號倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.60,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說No.104？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說No.105？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就相當棘手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.65,0:03:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人在碼頭的倉庫對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.31,0:03:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 絕對沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.82,0:03:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.79,0:03:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒准備的就衝進去太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.57,0:03:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先制定作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這份閑心 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把手機帶上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃離帝都的時候和懲罰部隊打得都這麼辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們倆的話一定沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.43,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.94,0:03:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一身酒臭…喂 我說你在干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不勝酒力…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.26,0:03:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是白痴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人都跑了 趕緊去抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.41,0:04:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花宴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.36,0:04:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊 別小看…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰部隊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懲罰部隊啊 懲罰部隊可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙已經沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:45.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 差不多該認真上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好我也這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了 結
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 比買東西競賽時快得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.73,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.09,0:05:07.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妾身必會救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 有兩手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是從容的時候哦 大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 我看上去這麼老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小搓衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搓衣板？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…搓衣板…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.44,0:05:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.16,0:05:57.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是主動看到呢…還是被動看到了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被夏朗之外的男人看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.94,0:06:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要宰了你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦啦 這個還是有點糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對二你覺得能贏過我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.44,0:06:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰翅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干毛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是個廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.70,0:06:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.23,0:06:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,激震
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葦牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.52,0:07:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的把No.88叫來不就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作…振作點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和鹡鸰或者葦牙沒關系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.42,0:07:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我要有人要受傷這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.69,0:07:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.26,0:07:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不想再有那種回憶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.68,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…這就是他的想法啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等的純粹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 是不需要理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.77,0:07:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.08,0:08:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要我嗎？我不會這樣問你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.53,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…想要你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…風花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為我擔心 為我哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.53,0:08:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 愛我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們鹡鸰需要的就是這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你身上吹來的風雖然還有些不太可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.11,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時間說早上好？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近總是睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎挺安靜的 大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎風招展了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你終於要成為最後一個羽化的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一個…難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 該准備晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 美哉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.21,0:09:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱 在我身體內一股熱流在亂竄
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他的思念 正在火熱的溫柔的融化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 我對他的思念 似乎終於可以停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.74,0:09:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽化…了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的契約之風 吹散葦牙之烏雲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:51.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花嵐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡了 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.17,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.34,0:10:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎…之前也遇到過這種情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.36,0:10:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 給我記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.78,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰No.03 風花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.69,0:10:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認同你是我的葦牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的戀情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的…鯉魚…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.97,0:10:26.08,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（和戀愛同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在一起 我的葦牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個怎麼在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝等到底在干什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.65,0:10:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花也羽化了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月…月海 小結
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.48,0:10:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:10:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人好厲害 這是第五羽鹡鸰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝和我說的失戀的事咋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不是說過了嗎 喜歡是不需要理由的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汝 適可而止點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 之前我應該說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.59,0:11:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能對我用這種口氣說話的只有No.01和這個游戲的主人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 大家要好好相處
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葦牙君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:44.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算有意思的節目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 結女沒能趕上真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可惜…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然打不通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.59,0:11:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:12:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 哥哥這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 嗯 還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 突然有急事來不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…為什麼媽媽會打電話過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 我不會對她們怎麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這樣和美哉說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.49,0:13:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.91,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.17,0:13:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼體的No.88被特工奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.57,0:13:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.44,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戀知鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這似乎是鹡鸰的別名
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是相愛就越強大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終有一天會展翅高飛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳導於世間愛為何物的鳥兒們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼偏離了這份堅持的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要保護好那些雛鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是緣之鹡鸰 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把愛…把愛教給這些小鳥們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.20,0:14:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你醒過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡在疼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是 醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.45,0:14:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBI直營的帝都醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人告訴我們在這裡葦牙是能免費看病的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.29,0:14:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你們 誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎沒有傷到腦子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於頭部撞傷造成的一時的意識障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩三天就能出院了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有點瘦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有好好吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 嗯 有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我和由香理約了要見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經告訴她你因為急事而去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.96,0:14:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽小結說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.42,0:14:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.96,0:15:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼媽媽會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.05,0:15:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說高美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是皆人的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們認識老媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.08,0:15:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要從哪裡說起好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前和你說過我在制藥公司工作過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 那個是騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是MBI鹡鸰計劃主任佐橋高美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據醫療措施 現在將對佐橋皆人進行臨時看護
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.19,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MBI?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結也是經過高美調整出來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.61,0:15:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調…調整！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.02,0:15:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換下水
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.93,0:15:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人 有些事想問下你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:15:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.30,0:16:02.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然想見見小結
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.57,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然知道我在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要在公司的話就能知道各種情報
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以高美才知道發生了什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.26,0:16:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒和紅翼打上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.35,0:16:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.63,0:16:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你煽動她們的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說小結有一段時間機能停止了沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小結似乎不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰紋曾經一度消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.02,0:16:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後身體發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:48.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我No.08緣之鹡鸰結女來做你們的對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.08!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機能停止後的再啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在腹部浮現出No.08的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時不明的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:17:01.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.08到底是何方神聖啊 高美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了不得不說這句的時候了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.12,0:17:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的時候要尊稱母親大人不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.21,0:17:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.06,0:17:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.08,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候你在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意了 這是我月海一生的恥辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母…母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個只是開玩笑而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海 冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.69,0:17:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於No.08不明的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結自身也有點特別情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結自身的特殊情況是？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LV4的鹡鸰 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先這樣 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…老媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.41,0:17:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回收隊的人有派過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LV4是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.09,0:18:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是指的距離機能停止的受損程度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等級分為五個階段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,LV4 傷得還真是夠重了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.48,0:18:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.03,0:18:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有血的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.17,0:18:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小結啊 要變得更加更加強大才行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:30.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那位一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.68,0:18:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 要比那位還要強大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後實現那個約定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.19,0:18:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們成為最後的兩羽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後賭上整個世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前就盡情的相互殘殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.22,0:18:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉羽大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.38,0:18:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是佐橋先生的出院慶祝會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.11,0:19:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不著這麼誇張啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 沒什麼大礙真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草非常非常的擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 小草
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.24,0:19:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過妾身這次的確太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然因為我的錯而使葦牙受傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.08,0:19:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月海…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是災難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈿女小姐 讓你擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.55,0:19:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說鹡鸰有增加了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.85,0:19:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加…鈿女小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是好厲害 哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來沒看見風花小姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 風花小姐的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來 皆人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…風花小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.84,0:20:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 這就是傳說中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.25,0:20:23.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 對新婚妻子還要加個小姐什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要叫我…風…花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.22,0:20:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出雲莊是禁止裸體圍裙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.39,0:20:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…美哉 好恐怖的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No.19 被黑色的鹡鸰給…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.17,0:20:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 還有風花…No.03已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.12,0:20:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們還不是不想觸怒北之般若
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以北部地區的狩獵行動都讓我來做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過相對的 千穂的病…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈿女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.44,0:21:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個不行啊 美哉說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再讓我看看你的收藏品嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.44,0:21:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 隨便挑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.21,0:21:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的有好多種類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿什麼才能讓皆人高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.73,0:21:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹡鸰紋 按著這裡詠唱祝詞的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你終於要成為最後一個羽化的了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會屬於任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有這個打算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.91,0:23:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是第五羽鹡鸰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.66,0:23:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皆人你想開後宮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.54,0:23:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就是後宮主管咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.71,0:23:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說妾在想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.13,0:23:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你連端茶送水都不成體統
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 所以說最近的年輕人真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.48,0:23:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.88,0:23:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能會說嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第四羽 最後的一羽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.58,0:23:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也要一直在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:10.43,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新しい約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:14.01,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}魂を強く繋ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}変わる世界に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.10,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鐘が響く ゆこう！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:24.45,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終りなき鬥いが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:28.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}すべてを引き裂いても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.13,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君の微笑み　ただ信じて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:38.39,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（あの日の）君の夢　守れるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:42.00,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（涙も）痛みさえ抱きしめよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:48.08,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（刻もう）重ね合うこの思い 胸の誓い
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:51.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}譲れない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:58.06,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああ　空の遙か涯てまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.80,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう　翔けてゆくような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.19,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}加速してく情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.29,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}ああ　どんな運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:16.67,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そう　高く越えてく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.38,OPJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}負けない勇気 くれたから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.41,0:00:10.43,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}新的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:14.01,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}將彼此靈魂緊緊相連
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.67,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在這變幻的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.00,0:00:21.10,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鐘聲響徹 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:24.45,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}即使無盡的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.68,0:00:28.08,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}將一切毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.13,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我會單純相信 你的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.32,0:00:38.39,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（那一天的）如果 能夠守護你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:42.00,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（即使流淚）我甘願承受苦難
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.22,0:00:48.08,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（銘刻吧）這份思念 在心頭交織 胸中的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:51.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}絕不退讓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.62,0:00:58.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}啊 直到那天空的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:02.80,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 就用那猶如飛翔一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.99,0:01:06.19,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷加速的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:12.29,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}啊 無論是何種命運
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:16.67,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 都能遠遠地超越過去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:23.38,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}因為是你給了我不服輸的勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:52.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命なんてね　全部ね　君次第
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:52.08,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運什麼的 全部 都依你而變
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.72,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついてく　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:55.72,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟隨你 無論到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.51,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同じ気持ちを　抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.51,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著相同的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:17.64,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,まだ誰にも発見されていない未知の大陸に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.86,0:22:17.64,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向還未被任何人發現的未知大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.06,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そぅ 一番先に踏み出すような
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.98,0:22:21.06,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一個邁出腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.66,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒険なの この戀は きっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.21,0:22:23.66,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去冒險 這份戀情 一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:25.60,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真実だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.85,0:22:25.60,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.65,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じてること 全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:28.65,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠感受到一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:34.61,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その聲が　今呼んでいるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:34.61,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聲音現在在呼喚著我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:39.15,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無謀だと わかってても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.30,0:22:39.15,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明知這樣很無謀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:42.33,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一緒に ためしたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:42.33,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是還是想要一起去嘗試
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:48.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何にも要らない　ねぇ　君が笑う度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.85,0:22:48.94,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不需要 每當你露出笑容的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:55.03,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生きてる その意味は　解き明かされて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.35,0:22:55.03,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生存下去的意義就此明了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:01.08,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命なんてね　全部ね　君次第
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.25,0:23:01.08,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運什麼的 全部 都依你而變
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.94,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ついてく　どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.94,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會跟隨你 無論到天涯海角
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.85,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同じ気持ちを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.19,0:23:07.85,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著相同的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:13.10,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強い気持ちを　抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.19,0:23:13.10,EDCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懷著強烈的情感
